In [10]:
import tensorflow as tf

labels = ['NORMAL', 'COVID']
X= []
y = []

for name in Normal_images_list:
  y.append(0)
  img = cv2.imread(name)
  img = tf.keras.preprocessing.image.img_to_array(img)
  img = cv2.resize(img,(128,128))
  X.append((img))

for name in covid_images_list:
  y.append(1)
  img = cv2.imread(name)
  img = tf.keras.preprocessing.image.img_to_array(img)
  img = cv2.resize(img,(128,128))
  X.append((img))
